import './style/App.css'
import React from 'react'
import Header from './components/header'
import Contacts from './components/contacts'
import HomePage from './pages/HomePage'
import NomersPage from './pages/NomersPage'

function App() {
	return (
		<>
			<Header />
			<HomePage />
			<NomersPage />
			<Contacts />
		</>
	)
}

export default App
